x4freetext: A thin self-supporting Al films, thickness about
50-mug/cm**2, evaporated in vacuum onto a thin Teepol
backing, which was disolved in water after evaporation.
Two targets were used during the experiments. The
thicknesses of both targets are quite uniform.
